<item>
  <title>HEAD OF DEPARTMENT-DEPARTMENT OF EMERGENCY MEDICINE</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/head-department-department-emergency-medicine</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;HEAD OF DEPARTMENT-DEPARTMENT OF EMERGENCY MEDICINE&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;a title="View user profile." href="https://www.ub.bw/user/1558" lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/1558" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" class="username" xml:lang=""&gt;ramahobok&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden"&gt;Fri, 11/02/2022 - 19:57&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-department field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Department/Faculty&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Emergency Medicine&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;FACULTY OF MEDICINE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;DEPARTMENT OF EMERGENCY MEDICINE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;HEAD OF DEPARTMENT (CONTRACT POSITION)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;VACANCY NO: FM/DEM01/2022&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The University of Botswana (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.ub.bw"&gt;www.ub.bw&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;) is the largest and most prestigious institution of higher learning in the country. It has opened the country’s first Faculty of Medicine and is affiliated to an adjacent new state-of-art 450-bed, the Sir Ketumile Masire Teaching Hospital. The first MBBS undergraduate intake was in August 2009. Undergraduate medical training is by a Problem Based Learning [PBL] Hybrid approach, which is integrated and community oriented. The Faculty of Medicine runs a number of Masters of Medicine (MMed) (residency) programmes, including Emergency Medicine and Psychiatry. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duties: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;the successful candidates will be expected to: (i)provide overall leadership and coordination of the department for efficient implementation of quality teaching and learning, research, and patient care; (ii) ensure successful delivery of the department’s mandate through effective budgeting and prudent resource management; (iii) to develop and manage the departmental human capital; (iv) work closely with the Ministry of Health and Wellness to facilitate the country to meet the sustainable development goals in their area of specialty; (v) create and maintain a high performance and ethical culture; (vi) effectively contribute to the faculty and institutional strategic goals;  (vii) participate in the faculty’s management processes including staff recruitment, assessment and promotion, students’ assessment, and research management; (viii) perform any other duty as may be assigned by the Dean and; (ix) act for the Deputy Deans/Dean as may be required; (x) participate in institutional activities as the need may rise from time to time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Heads of Department report to the Dean, Faculty of Medicine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Qualification and Experience: (i) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;an undergraduate medical degree and a specialist qualification in Emergency Medicine with a minimum of 6 years of post-specialization professional practice in as an Emergency Physician. The qualification must be registerable by the Botswana Health Professions Council with a specialist status; (ii) must have attained the academic rank of senior lecturer or higher in the preceding 12 months prior to appointment; (iii) 1 year of distinctive record of leadership and administration of university level institution or Head of Department is desirable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Attributes and skills required; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(i)&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;excellent communication and organizational skills; (ii) strong academic leadership skills and sympathy for the values and culture of the University; (iii) good management, human relations, sound analytical and coordinating skills; (iv) clinical excellence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duration of the contracts:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  the above positions are available for restricted term contracts of three years and maybe renewed for a further term of three years on the basis of satisfactory performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Remuneration:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; the University offers competitive salaries and benefits commensurate with experience and qualifications.  For more information on the University, please visit our website; &lt;a href="http://www.ub.bw"&gt;www.ub.bw&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to apply&lt;/strong&gt;: applicants are to address the stated qualifications and provide other information to assist the University determine their suitability.  They should provide current CVs (including telephone and e-mail), certified copies of educational certificates and transcripts, and three (3) reference letters. Complete documentation should be sent to: &lt;strong&gt;The Human Resources Manager, Faculty of Medicine, Corner of Notwane and Mabuto Road, University of Botswana, Private Bag 00713 Gaborone, Botswana; or Email to &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:tshoganetsom@ub.ac.bw"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;tshoganetsom@ub.ac.bw&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants should inform their referees to:  (i) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;quote the position applied for and &lt;strong&gt;(ii)&lt;/strong&gt; submit their references directly to the address above. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA" xml:lang="EN-ZA"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hand delivered applications should be sent to &lt;strong&gt;Faculty of Medicine, UB Teaching Hospital, 3rd Floor, Office F4003/3004.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing date: Open until filled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

