  <title>ASSISTANT PROGRAMME DIRECTOR (3 YEAR RESTRICTED-TERM CONTRACT)</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/assistant-programme-director-3-year-restricted-term-contract</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;ASSISTANT PROGRAMME DIRECTOR (3 YEAR RESTRICTED-TERM CONTRACT)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;span lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/2085" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" xml:lang=""&gt;maribek&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden"&gt;Thu, 27/02/2020 - 16:37&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-department field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Department/Faculty&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Emergency Medicine&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-tender-closing-date field--type-datetime field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
